Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've...finally made it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they still haven't been able\Nto find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This hideout is rather large,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be\Na struggle for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a different story\Nif they had a detailed map...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately,\Nit's inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think if you said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd ask you to show me\Nthe way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission is to stand guard\Nover you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no intention of doing\Nsomething so risky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as to take you inside your base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last room\Non this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're split up\Ninto two search teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay calm\Nand rest a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close...to Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The damage I took when I morphed\N{\i1}into the Nine-Tails still hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not in here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...\NYou're getting too impatient...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the inside\Nof Orochimaru's hideout...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that traps\Nhave been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get too impatient,\Nhe might find out that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But! Sasuke is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Naruto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only a matter of time\Nbefore we find Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Act with caution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:56.43,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(677,602)}The Picture Book's Story\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you're awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy...you really resemble him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was talkative and\Nhe would lose his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no manners...\Nand his equipment was--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah...like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he went all-out with\Neverything he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of remember him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...! Hey, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered...\NI remembered...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I wanted\Nto show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture of our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which side are you going\Nto take?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought. It seems\Nyou're taking that side, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you go find Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I'll find Sasuke...\Nand save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came to take back\NSasuke, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your persistence is impressive,\Nbut will it really be that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any difference that\Nyou're one of the Legendary Sannin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like the Pervy Sage and\NGrandma Tsunade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat you...\Nand take Sasuke back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto's Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears something\Nhas happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to all\Nyour energy from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power...\NThe power of the Nine-Tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be more to it\Nthan this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one\N{\i1}who hurt Sakura, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll end up tormenting yourself\N{\i1}if you rely on the power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the Nine-Tails from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it could turn into a power\N{\i1}that hurts your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like what happened this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to save Sasuke,\N{\i1}do it with your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you want to see Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}do it with your own eyes,\N{\i1}not the Nine-Tails'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if you want\N{\i1}to protect Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}do it with your own power,\N{\i1}not the Nine-Tails'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru again, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto is stalling Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm sure the Captain\N{\i1}and Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have gone to back up Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Super Beast Scroll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still let you live...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dispose of as many members\Nof the Akatsuki as you can, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\NI've got business with Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai's looking for Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something\Nbefore Orochimaru finds him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to use up all of\Nmy Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll try searching with\Nmy Multiple Shadow Clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato and Sakura,\Nyou guys search that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He...was able to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that's the picture of dreams\Nhe wanted to show his older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... He smiled for real for\Nthe first time when he drew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiled from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in Sai's bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an assassination list\Nthat has...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,an Anbu Black Ops member's\Nown targets recorded...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a Bingo Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An assassination list...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these "X" marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they're marks indicating targets\Nthat have already been eliminated...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Sai have such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Sasuke's face...\Nin Sai's assassination list...?
